headline: Has Uber’s 243% Three Year Surge Left Further Upside For Investors In 2025
summary: Wondering if Uber Technologies is still worth buying after its huge run, or if the easy money has already been made? This overview cuts through the noise and focuses on what the current price is really implying. Uber’s share price has climbed 5.7% over the last week and 46.5% year to date, adding to an impressive 42.5% gain over the past year and 243.1% over three years.
